    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and is entirely free of chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, with the leather upholstery still firm and the interior trim completely unmarked. Mechanically, the car is perfect; it has been meticulously maintained with a complete service history, and every component functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment.",
      "price": 49500.0,
