    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering an exceptional synthesis of performance and long-term value. This specimen has been curated to meet rigorous standards, ensuring a driving experience characterized by mechanical precision and aesthetic preservation. Featuring a comprehensive service history and a well-appointed interior, this automobile represents a premier opportunity for the professional seeking a dependable yet sophisticated addition to their fleet.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) equipped with the S54B32 high-revving straight-six and a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically sorted, featuring documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Besian systems components. To address the chassis's inherent weak points, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with epoxy-injected plates. Performance is maintained via a factory limited-slip differential and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing Bilstein dampers. While the Titanium Silver finish displays minor patina and stone chips commensurate with enthusiast use, the powertrain remains tight with linear power delivery and no timing chain rattle. A solid, turn-key M-car for the purist who values mechanical integrity over concours aesthetics.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Reliable engine. Clean title. Minor interior wear. All maintenance records available.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the slightest signs of road use consistent with a well-cared-for car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery shows minimal wear, and every feature\u2014from the responsive climate control to the crisp audio system\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a strict preventative maintenance schedule that ensures a smooth, confident ride. It has been primarily garage-kept and recently underwent a full professional detailing. It is a turn-key example ready for its next journey, offering the peace of mind that comes with a documented service history and a clean title.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic, it offers a balanced combination of performance and reliability. Every aspect of this automobile has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for quality and roadworthiness. We invite you to experience the superior handling and sophisticated interior that define this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next big adventure? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own! It's in solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It runs beautifully and is just waiting for a new driver to hit the road. I'd love to chat and answer any questions you have\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six engine. This A80 chassis maintains its sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, providing smooth boost transition through the RPM range. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a factory helical limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a timing belt replacement, new valve cover gaskets to address common seepage, and a cooling system flush. The suspension utilizes OEM-spec Bilstein dampers, preserving the original handling characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders and the turbo seals remain tight with no evidence of oil blow-by. A driver-focused example that performs exactly as a flagship grand tourer should.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
